data.description: Come home to this showstopper and the most popular four-bedroom floorplan in the quiet master-planned community of Anna Town Square. This TV-ready home has all bedrooms downstairs with a private game room and an additional full bathroom upstairs that could easily be used as an additional fifth bedroom. The home comes equipped with a tankless water heater, gas throughout, and more. You also cannot miss the additional designer details in this home that add the character unmatched by neighboring homes. The large backyard can easily accommodate a pool or tramp-o-line. Feel free to view the MATTERPORT virtual tour to see this home from your phone or computer prior to visiting.
